      "text": "A company’s approach to scaling is inimitable, arbitrary structures and processes may be easily copied but the fundamental interrelationships cannot ([[Martin Reeves et al. 2020]]).\nA copy-and-paste approach to implementing large-scale policy and organisational reform in one system, based on best practices from another setting, rarely produces the desired results ([[Lant Pritchett et al. 2010]]; [[Matt Andrews et al. 2013]])."
